      "created_at": "2024-09-17T11:52:34.468Z",
      "cooked": "<p>We have a flux s we use in testing and have never seen this issue (or not recently anyway) but for sure we still do have some connection issues at times with some devices.  Phone restart should fix it.  We are continually working to improve how connections work. Sorry about that.  Hopefully it does not happen again. As I said it does not happen to our Flux S\u2026 I am going to ask my tester right now to make 100% sure I am telling the truth <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>",
