      "created_at": "2024-09-17T12:12:43.971Z",
      "cooked": "<p>My tester asked if you used the latest version of our app that came out yesterday and if you happened to switch between slope and ERG mode.  If you had the previous version (not the new one from yesterday afternoon/evening depending on where you were in the world) he said it was possible as we had a new bug recently.  This should be fixed if you update today and hopefully you will never see this again.  If you do, phone restart to save some frustration and please let me know if it is fixed or you see this again.</p>",
